title: Ep. 137 - Why I'm Bullish On The Euro

description: Keith Fitz-Gerald, chief investment strategist at Money Map Press, says Europe will come through the crisis stronger than ever. Frank breaks down big banks and tells us why most companies in this specific industry may not exist over the next 18 months.
